FYI here's a link to an MG (the British car, that is) parts supplier in
Massachusetts that sells Waxoyl:

http://www.propermg.com/wax104.htm

It's available with a pump sprayer, or as an aerosol.  It seems to be
like a mixture of mineral spirits, beeswax, and machine oil.

